WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.600
Okay, so KG Engineering is a specialist company that services your manufacturing industries,

00:07.600 --> 00:15.800
your agricultural industries, anything to do with repairs and maintenance of valves, pneumatics,

00:15.800 --> 00:24.880
hydraulics, boilers, LPG gas lines, all industrial aspects of your manufacturing process.

00:24.880 --> 00:32.320
We can assist with supply of material, installation of material and also refurbishment of material.

00:32.320 --> 00:38.200
Inquiries are generated via site visits mainly, but obviously we would still like to look

00:38.200 --> 00:41.560
into websites and referrals.

00:41.560 --> 00:48.440
So what eats up most of my time is invoicing statements and also following up on quotations

00:48.440 --> 00:56.280
from suppliers as this is very time-consuming calls, emails, regularly, WhatsApps as well

00:56.280 --> 01:04.160
to suppliers, then also follow-ups to clients regarding quotes submitted and projects submitted

01:04.160 --> 01:06.840
as well.

01:06.840 --> 01:11.760
Things that frustrate me the most would be not issuing out statements and invoices

01:11.760 --> 01:18.480
on time as this eats away cash flow and it's always delayed on my side as there's quite

01:18.480 --> 01:21.280
a bit going on in the background.

01:21.280 --> 01:28.600
So the software that I currently use now is Zoho invoicing software and also WhatsApp

01:28.600 --> 01:30.760
for client.

01:30.760 --> 01:34.920
Clients contact me directly via WhatsApp if they need me to come to site or even quote

01:34.920 --> 01:41.120
on items they are fully understood about what they require.

01:41.120 --> 01:47.320
Usually a typical job goes like this, we go to site, we generate the inquiry, we come

01:47.320 --> 01:52.520
back, we do research, if research is needed on items that we are not familiar with, we

01:52.520 --> 01:57.600
quote and then we either supply or we onsite with the installation work.

